Package: everyfind
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, python3-pip, fzf, gettext
Description: Ultra-fast file search for Linux with multilingual GTK GUI
 Everyfind is a blazing-fast file search tool for Linux, inspired by
 "Everything" on Windows. It combines fzf speed with a GTK interface.
 .
 Features:
  - Lightning-fast fuzzy search powered by fzf
  - Dual interfaces: CLI and GTK GUI
  - Multilingual support (German, English, French, Spanish, Polish)
  - SQLite indexing for instant results
  - Configurable filters and auto-reindexing
  - Raspberry Pi compatible (ARM support)

